        <h3><u>~ About this project ~</u></h3>
        <p>I started this project with zero web development experience nor any knowledge of html/css. After watching some tutorials online, I figured I should try it out myself! For this project, I only used css and html to keep it simple. 
            I really enjoyed playing around with UI; I wanted to develope a night time, chic interface that granted the customer with a feel for 'The Fountain', 
